  </div>

  <h2>🧠 Final Advice: Stay Smart, Stay Safe</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Don't click suspicious links</li>
    <li>Never share OTPs or passwords</li>
    <li>Update your apps and systems</li>
    <li>Use strong, unique passwords</li>
    <li>Don’t trust random “tech support” calls</li>
  </ul>

